<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="95" type="threats">
<paragraph pageId="2" pageNumber="95">Threats.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="2" pageNumber="95">
Threats to this species include invasive alien plant species, primarily 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Axonopus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Axonopus fissifolius" order="Poales" pageId="2" pageNumber="95" phylum="Angiospermae" rank="species" species="fissifolius">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">Axonopus fissifolius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Raddi) Kuhlm., 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Lour" authorityYear="1790" class="Dicotyledoneae" family="Loganiaceae" genus="Buddleja" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Buddleja asiatica" order="Gentianales" pageId="2" pageNumber="95" phylum="Angiospermae" rank="species" species="asiatica">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">Buddleja asiatica</emphasis>
